comments.body:
Nit: suggest adding a comment to `unsigned char fingerprint[4];` above:
```
// BIP32 defines the key identifier as the RIPEMD160 after SHA256 of
// the serialized ECDSA public key K, ignoring the chain code. The first 32 bits
// of this is the key fingerprint.
```

